creator: Swan General Ltd
descriptionHtml:
MySwan is the free app from Swan for a seamless access to various services around your insurance products anytime, anywhere !

MySwan users having Internet Access on their smartphone will be able to:

· View and monitor their Health insurance, Home insurance, Car insurance and Life policies.
· Submit health claims.
· Submit motor claims notifications.
· View digital version of SWAN cards for Health, Travel and Rewards
· View accounts.
· Request quotes
· Locate Swan branches
· Call Swan Assistance

Follow these simple steps to start using MySwan
1. Download MySwan on your phone
2. Register using your Swan Direct credentials
3. Enter your 4 digit mPIN

Now your Swan insurance is within your fingertips!

Stay tuned for innovative updates on MySwan!

For more details, please visit www.swanforlife.com or contact us on +230 207 3500.

Call our hotline on 207 9111 between 09:30 to 18:30 from Monday to Friday and on Saturday from 09:30 to 17:00.
You can also email us on myswan.appsupport@swanforlife.com.
